DESCRIPTION: Export all the feedback into a CSV file after a certain feedback message using the feedback id.
EXTENDED_LINE_1: **${prefix}export [Message ID] [#Channel]** ~ Exports all feedback sent in that channel after the feedback with ID of 1
EXTENDED_LINE_2: Note: The Channel option will only accept either the bug channel or the idea channel from your feedback. Also due to discord limits, we can only export a maximum of 100 messages.
ALIASES: Export does not have any aliases.
CSV: Here is your CSV file to easily export your feedback. Cheers!
